{"tid":1476260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.","createTime":"2019-08-15T18:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T04:55:06.000Z","uid":268251,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9df8e185a715ad8689ed3d8b402395bbf3277e","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:10:14.000Z","msg":"發夢左咁耐, 係咪應該搵一首支持我地信念既歌, 去將我地既信念帶俾全世界呢?<br />\n仲記得當初我地唱Do you hear the people sing, 個感染力比呢兩個星期既新聞感染力更大.<br />\n我地既初心, 係反送中, 與其成日俾官媒話我地暴力, 我地就用歌聲去將我地既理念唱出去.<br />\n我揀左一首歌, 歌詞係對自由既響往, 對抗官媒暴力既抹黑, 呢首歌絕對可以反擊.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歌聲+歌詞, 絕對比我地口講既力量大好撚多!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以聽住黎睇歌詞. 覺得好, 請正評並推post.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Il7Tp2r9qL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIl7Tp2r9qL8&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=f4a8ad79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Il7Tp2r9qL8</a><br />\n<br />\nLiberty stands for freedom<br />\nOh hail the flag that set us free<br />\nstanding righteous symbolic of<br />\nstrength our hopes for freedom to be.<br />\nMy friends reunite hand in hand<br />\nOh hail! Liberty bell!<br />\nTrue freedom for all men.<br />\n<br />\nFighting hard for the future<br />\nThe promise of a better day<br />\nFor tomorrow we drink from the cup,<br />\nthe wine we fought for today<br />\nmy friends, let us sing a song<br />\nsing a long ring a bell, liberty!<br />\nOh hail! Liberty bell!<br />\nTrue freedom for all men.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;F&quot; that stands for our freedom<br />\nas well the flag that stands so strong<br />\nSprite set free in our future land,<br />\nso let us share in this song<br />\nMy friends, not so far away<br />\nRules will reunite hand in hand<br />\nOh hail! Liberty bell!<br />\nTrue freedom for all men."},{"pid":"790c5dbf5bdb58dfdfd3841f71d64357b4346d2a","tid":1476260,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c5293ac887b0596d11604b9a8e321a56dbd4a38","tid":1476260,"uid":248057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"對付中國網友必殺技 （已測試超有效）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"197c4bd5a8e74a9f61567e1bccd722c1c2a4f46d","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:13:25.000Z","msg":"我地如果靜坐, 係可以唱呢首歌, 派埋歌詞俾旅客,<br />\n絕對比靜坐或同黑警打交更加有效果!"},{"pid":"eaca4a5010af6f7855833ace479b344dd0d28cb2","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"905416c306cd7e86effac008c3a0d04c95dae9c7","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"推到有人回"},{"pid":"b554490b87b6c3d22e487ab29fc81bf293f8657d","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b55827ffe7fe5a2fbd532420b53a3735f12eee71","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3b23772b0973e9dd57af03e2e6939c0dfc6cd0b","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32dc6a600287e612472c507ea48985236c0ddab","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"769f2dd6d7dc6f8dbd9b672c1968fdee62e096be","tid":1476260,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dd7c5232b63766